<hymn_number>167</hymn_number>
<title>HIGHER GROUND</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Chnglam ah ka kalto zel hi,
 Nichenga sang to deuh deuh in;
 Chieh zelin ka paucham zing hi,
 &quot;Lalpa mun sangzaw ei tunin.&quot;

[V2]
 Ei pui to in, ei din sakin,
 Ginan'n Van thamzawl nuom achun;
 Munsang leh nuom zaw tun ka nuom,
 Lalpa mun sangzaw ei tunin.

[V3]
 2. Khawvel chung lama len ka nuom,
 Setan thalin ei kap mahleh;
 Ginna'n la ngaihnawp um ka za'i,
 Mun sangzaw a mithiengte la.

[V4]
 3. Mun sang pen tung thei leng ka nuom,
 Lopina vak chuh mu dingin;
 Van ka tun ma'n paucham zing ka,
 &quot;Mun sang zaw ah ei pui in&quot; ti'n.</lyrics>
</song>